{"tid":1478048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話渣美國旗冇用既手足，睇下當年清朝點評價美國同華盛頓","createTime":"2019-08-16T10:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T18:41:49.000Z","uid":80356,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e24bc8d459e00356071e6369893156cf68ddcfad","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"當年清朝進士徐繼畬係《瀛寰志略》提到美國國父華盛頓：<br />\n<br />\n按華盛頓，異人也。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>起事勇於勝廣，割據雄於曹劉</strong></span></span>，旣已提三尺劔，開疆萬里，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃不僭位號，不傳子孫，而創爲推舉之法，幾於天下為公，駸駸乎三代之遺意</span></span></strong>。　<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢到盛讚華盛頓有先秦堯舜虞三位天下共主的遺風</span></strong>　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇埋落去<br />\n其治國崇讓善俗，不尚武功，亦迥與諸國異。余嘗見其畫像，氣魄雄毅絕倫，嗚呼，可不謂人傑矣哉。米利堅合衆國以為國，<strong>幅員萬里，不設王侯之號，不循世及之規，公器付之公論</strong>，創古今未有之局，一何奇也？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">泰西古今人物，能不以華盛頓爲稱首哉！ </span></span></strong><br />\n早係清末徐繼畬就好有遠見，要全世界學習美國民主制度<br />\n不過擺係現代，佢係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勾結外國勢力份子</span>　<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到，好多人會問點解華盛頓唔食住個民意稱帝或者選埋第三屆<br />\n華盛頓咁講：<strong>一旦我這樣做將是可恥的</strong>，因為儘管這是我國同胞的願望，而且在大家的信任下我可能當選並任職，但另一個比我更有才能的人卻會因此去職<br />\n再望下而家習大大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rE5Be9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrE5Be9G.jpg&h=6ab772fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因果由國<br />\n容港治己<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLxLSRq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLxLSRq.png&h=f2ce6685&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">STAND WITH HONG KONG <br />\nFIGHT FOR FREEDOM</span></span>"},{"pid":"d0a5609e2e2045c5a2f84bb51b1057a13c341729","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0948a4195eb8085def3fb3ae4d36f6af44ec37d9","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"87b347618e6362ec5ce25cf2d3b6865bf30cb5b7","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d1f0c2862e3c4acf9fc3b05b02bc82f89e1ed8cd","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3b2cd7aa5fc054c62e6ec47165b44ff2c063d41f","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:46:25.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a02532b16cecdebe47a0891b86fc6a9272615642","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:46:43.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"181a23b0c316fe46ef84f8ddf8008d8329e60b59","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"8ca20765f8f6cc2ae5bc8d081be6f6ef0dee2473","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8b1209ab1861a97a165f3dd936bd12a9abb8a071","tid":1478048,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"